#DOC id=19--asset-lab--leonardo-knowledge source=/root/yvon/docs/briefs/lifeos-reference/19--asset-lab--leonardo-knowledge.md format=toon-doc compressed=2026-06-12T06:40:26.303Z

S|# 19 · Asset Lab · Leonardo (Knowledge)|> The lab for the image-generation agt, **Leonardo**: every generated image in one place to view, download and reuse, plus **brand kits** (colors, logos, assets) per workspace.
S|Purpose|"The lab for my image generation model." A gallery + workbench where the owner can see everything **Leonardo** has created, reuse/download assets, and define **brand kits** (color schemes, logos, assets) for each workspace so generated imagery stays on-brand.
S|Page header|- Title: **Asset Lab**, breadcrumb `Vibe with AI / Asset Lab · Leonardo`. // - Sub-line: "Leonardo is rendering X concepts · 1,2XX assets saved across your brands." // - Top-right toggles: **Gallery**, **gen**, **Thumbnails** (modes/views). // - **Spend tracker** — cost figures for image generation, e.g. **$0.18 / $7.42 / $128.60** (last render / today / month), with a monthly budget note (e.g. "$129 / $200").
S|Filters & search|- **Search assets** ("neon thumbnail," "human that flat lay," "Maria hero," …). // - **Brand filter chips**: **All brands**, **Vibe**, **By Design**, **Valhalla**, etc. // - **Type filter chips**: **All types**, **Thumbnail**, **Post**, **Hero**, **Cinematic**, **Graphic**, etc.
S|Asset grid|- A masonry/grid of generated images, each tile showing the visual plus metadata: title (e.g. "Long-form thumb · big face, less text," "Cinematic Site hero — Maria project · cinematic dusk skyline," "The 5-asset stack"), the **brand/workspace**, **type**, a **cost** (e.g. $1.7/$1.2), and a relative time. // - Tile actions: **download**, **reuse**, and inspect what Leonardo was working with.
S|Brand Kit (right rail)|- **Brand Kit** panel scoped to a workspace ("All brands" / per-brand): //   - **Display / style** settings (e.g. "Space Mood"). //   - **Ratio** presets. //   - **Personas / brand persona** assets (e.g. "Nina · brand persona") used to keep generated humans consistent. //   - **Colors, logos, assets** for each workspace's brand identity.
S|Agent & integrations|- **Leonardo** is the image-generation agt; outputs here feed **soc Approvals** (the 8 candidate images per post), **YouTube Studio** (thumbnails), **Cinematic Sites** (hero imagery), etc. // - Cost/budget tracking is built in so image-gen spend stays controlled.